title: Gogglebox NZ
overview: Gogglebox is BAFTA award-winning international reality TV show that's coming to New Zealand...Ever wonder what other people are saying about your favourite show? Are they voicing exactly what you've been thinking, or does their view shed a refreshing new light on popular culture? Sit tight, because all your questions will soon be answered.Once a week, the spotlight will be on 11 ordinary Kiwi households, as cameras capture their reactions while they watch TV from the previous week.
